est. And here’s the thing: I would totally even consider this tortellini salad a snack. An actual SNACK. I can’t tell you how many times I grab a bowl of it from the fridge… for a snack. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYep. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"salami and red pepper tortellini salad\" width=\"1697\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/best-tortellini-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"The Tortellini Salad I’m Making All Summer Long.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-scaled.jpg 1697w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-728x944.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-768x996.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-1185x1536.jpg 1185w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-1580x2048.jpg 1580w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1697px) 100vw, 1697px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201697%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-scaled.jpg 1697w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-728x944.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-768x996.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-1185x1536.jpg 1185w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-1580x2048.jpg 1580w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-3-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe thing is, I make a lot of tortellini salads that we enjoy. This \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2019/12/cilantro-lime-tortellini-salad/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecopycat one from the nordstrom e-bar\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e is incredible. My \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/06/chicken-tortellini-pasta-salad/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003esummer chicken tortellini salad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e is great too. And \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2022/04/chickpea-tortellini-salad/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ethe lunchtime chickpea version\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e is a staple for my own meals. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBut this one takes the cake. Or the pasta. Or the salads! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt’s truly the best cheese tortellini salad I have ever tasted. Eddie kept calling it an antipasto tortellini salad, and it does have a similar flavor profile. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt is just delicious!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"salami and red pepper tortellini salad\" width=\"1753\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/best-tortellini-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"The Tortellini Salad I’m Making All Summer Long.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-scaled.jpg 1753w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-728x913.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-768x964.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-1224x1536.jpg 1224w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-1632x2048.jpg 1632w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-150x188.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1753px) 100vw, 1753px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201753%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-scaled.jpg 1753w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-728x913.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-768x964.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-1224x1536.jpg 1224w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-1632x2048.jpg 1632w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-150x188.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHere’s what we’re working with:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCheese tortellini, of course. Whatever variety you love works. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSalami, diced up. You could also use a spicy one! I’m a baby. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBaby arugula greens. They are peppery and perfect. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShallots, diced into tiny chunks! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRoasted red peppers – quite possibly my favorite pantry ingredient. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFeta cheese. The crumbled kind is perfect here. So tangy and creamy. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-99389\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"salami and red pepper tortellini salad\" width=\"1728\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/best-tortellini-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"The Tortellini Salad I’m Making All Summer Long.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-scaled.jpg 1728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-728x927.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-768x978.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-1207x1536.jpg 1207w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-1609x2048.jpg 1609w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-150x191.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1728px) 100vw, 1728px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201728%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-scaled.jpg 1728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-728x927.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-768x978.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-1207x1536.jpg 1207w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-1609x2048.jpg 1609w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-150x191.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd a super delicious dressing that is tangy and briney and zesty and all around mouth-watering. Truly, my italian vinaigrette is packed with fresh garlic and red wine vinegar. It is not for the faint of heart! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"salami and red pepper tortellini salad\" width=\"1626\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/best-tortellini-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"The Tortellini Salad I’m Making All Summer Long.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-scaled.jpg 1626w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-728x985.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-768x1039.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-1135x1536.jpg 1135w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-1513x2048.jpg 1513w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-150x203.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1626px) 100vw, 1626px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201626%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-scaled.jpg 1626w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-728x985.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-768x1039.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-1135x1536.jpg 1135w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-1513x2048.jpg 1513w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-150x203.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMy favorite thing about a salad like this is that it is incredible even after it sits for a day. Sure, the tortellini soaks up most of the dressing, and it’s always a little tough straight from the fridge. But the flavors are fantastic, it’s satisfying and such a nice dish to make in the summer.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePool lunch? Easy dinner on the deck? Side dish for a BBQ? \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt works for all of these!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNow run run run and try it. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"salami and red pepper tortellini salad\" width=\"1686\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/best-tortellini-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"The Tortellini Salad I’m Making All Summer Long.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-scaled.jpg 1686w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-728x950.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-768x1002.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-1177x1536.jpg 1177w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-1569x2048.jpg 1569w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-150x196.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1686px) 100vw, 1686px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201686%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-scaled.jpg 1686w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-728x950.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-768x1002.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-1177x1536.jpg 1177w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-1569x2048.jpg 1569w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-150x196.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-8-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRoasted Red Pepper and Salami Tortellini Salad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-99400\" data-recipe-id=\"99400\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-4-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eRoasted Red Pepper and Salami Tortellini Salad\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"99400\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e25\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e5\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e25\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis is the best tortellini salad ever! Loaded with baby arugula greens, roasted red peppers, salami, feta cheese and more, it is so satisfying and such a delicious dish for dinner or a party. Make it today!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"99400\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e20\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echeese tortellini,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecooked\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3 to 5\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ebaby arugula greens\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/shallots-price-per-lb/-/A-14993271?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eshallots,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ediced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ejar roasted red peppers,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003edrained and chopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003esalami,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/athenos-crumbled-traditional-feta-cheese-4oz/-/A-13308538?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ecrumbled feta cheese\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eitalian vinaigrette\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pompeian-red-wine-vinegar-16-fl-oz/-/A-47846730?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ered wine vinegar\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/spice-world-fresh-whole-garlic-3ct-bag/-/A-14917318?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic cloves,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eminced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/dijon-mustard-12oz-market-pantry-8482/-/A-14766261?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edijon mustard\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"10\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-clover-honey-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-54436198?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ehoney\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"11\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-oregano-0-8oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77616564?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edried oregano\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"12\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/morton-coarse-kosher-salt-16oz/-/A-13170448?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ekosher salt\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"13\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efresh ground black pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"14\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-olive-oil-25-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77600361?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eolive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"99400\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99400-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eBring a pot of salted water to a boil and cook the tortellini according to the package directions. This should only take 3 or 4 minutes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99400-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlace the arugula in a large bowl. You can use however much or as little as you’d like - remember it will wilt down! When the tortellini is finished cooking, drain it. Place it on top of the arugula in the bowl. Gently toss. This will help the arugula wilt too.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99400-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd in the shallots, peppers, salami and feta. Drizzle in a few tablespoons of the dressing and toss gently. Dress more as desired. Serve!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99400-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eNote: this will make a lot of dressing but the key is to over-dress your pasta salad if you plan on keeping it in the fridge, serving it at a party or letting it sit for a bit. You can always save the dressing in the fridge!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99400-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eitalian vinaigrette\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99400-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhisk together the vinegar, garlic, dijon, honey, oregano, salt and pepper until combined. Stream in the olive oil while whisking until emulsified. This dressing stays great in the fridge for a week! Just whisk or shake before serving.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSalad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"salami and red pepper tortellini salad\" width=\"1713\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/best-tortellini-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"The Tortellini Salad I’m Making All Summer Long.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-scaled.jpg 1713w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-728x935.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-768x986.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-1196x1536.jpg 1196w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-1595x2048.jpg 1595w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-150x193.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1713px) 100vw, 1713px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201713%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-scaled.jpg 1713w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-728x935.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/tortellini-salad-with-salami-6-768x986.jpg